Title: Synopsis — The Tug of War
Sequence: Tug of War
Source: V5

===

~ The Alderman and Kestrel pull Fleur toward the coronation from opposite directions. The demon grows. Fleur walks in with her eyes open.

The Alderman grooms Fleur for the coronation as spectacle — the Chosen One crowned as Solar Queen, his dynasty legitimised. Kestrel advises from behind bars, positioning herself as the counterweight to the Alderman while steering Fleur toward the demon. The demon grows with each surrender. Each shortcut felt reasonable at the time. Fleur walks into the coronation with her eyes open, believing she can save the community she built through honest work. The demon erupts. The city burns.
